profile_positions.description:
I started working with the consultancy unit of HAS Den Bosch named HAS KennisTransfer. I was mainly focused on the Netherlands. We offered consultancy and training to organisations in food technology, environment, horticulture, animal husbandry, life sciences. From out of HAS KennisTransfer I worked for HAS Den Bosch as consultant in an international fact finding mission project. After a couple of years I had the chance to work for HAS Den Bosch only in the function of International Officer.

Tasks:
- Creating an international PR & recruitment plan;
- Account management for strategic partners/Campaigning;
- Fund acquisition: study grants, EU applications;
- Website: development, text and image provision, content management;
- Fairs: organisation, stand staffing, giving presentations;
- Project management, applying for international subsidies with partners;
- Advising executives on policy and strategic ad hoc decisions;
- Representing and fostering interests of HAS in umbrella committees;
- Acting head/management of Foreign Department.

As Manager Marketing Communications, I was responsible for the Northern Europe area. In close collaboration with sales, I was able to make McAfee visible in the markets and generated leads.  Together with an eager team and lots of fun, we were able to meet the targets and we branded McAfee as the global anti-virus and network management leader. 

Tasks:
- creating and implementing marketing communication plan with sales;
- account management for distributors and key resellers;
- advising management on strategy;
- initiating, participating in and co-organising fairs, seminars and other events in the Netherlands and Europe; giving product presentations;
- production/management of sales support material; 
- preparing, writing and/or translating press releases, contacts with the press; 
- generating free publicity;
- induction and supervision of pre-sales employees; 
- market (and competition) research; generating leads; 
- group target;
- budget responsibility.
